{"title":"css设置与嵌入视频设置","uid":"4864d840e4d205ca6b2000c95f62e1a3","slug":"aurora简解/css设置与嵌入视频设置","date":"2000-08-15T10:49:36.000Z","updated":"2023-01-13T20:15:06.046Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/aurora简解/css设置与嵌入视频设置.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/fengmian/20.jfif","content":"<h1 id=\"hexo-aurora的CSS怎么设置\"><a href=\"#hexo-aurora的CSS怎么设置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo-aurora的CSS怎么设置\"></a>hexo-aurora的CSS怎么设置</h1><p>首先我们要知道aurora的CSS设置与我们平时用的hexo创建的CSS有所不同<br>比方我们要嵌入哔哩哔哩视频我们该怎么设置并让他读取到我们要设置的CSS呢？<br>我们先找到我们想设置的CSS,例如我现在的这个嵌入哔哩哔哩视频适配CSS</p>\n<h4 id=\"哔哩哔哩视频适配CSS\"><a href=\"#哔哩哔哩视频适配CSS\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"哔哩哔哩视频适配CSS\"></a>哔哩哔哩视频适配CSS</h4><details class=\"custom-details\">\n<summary>CSS代码</summary>\n<p><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">/*哔哩哔哩视频适配*/</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>aspect<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>ratio <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">position</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> relative<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">width</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token operator\">%</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">height</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  padding<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>bottom<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">75</span><span class=\"token operator\">%</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">margin</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token operator\">%</span> auto<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  text<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>align<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> center<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>aspect<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>ratio iframe <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">position</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> absolute<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">width</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token operator\">%</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">height</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">86</span><span class=\"token operator\">%</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">left</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">top</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n</p>\n</details>\n<h4 id=\"主题CSS的文件目录\"><a href=\"#主题CSS的文件目录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"主题CSS的文件目录\"></a>主题CSS的文件目录</h4><p>然后进入我们的部署文件（目录\\node_modules\\hexo-theme-aurora\\source\\static\\css）找到名为：post.9f951a60.css文件<br><img src=\"/images%5C1%5C2.png\"><br>像这样，打开它<br><img src=\"/images%5C1%5C3.png\"><br>这是aurora主题页面的CSS，我们也可以拿来当作CSS文件<br>我们可以在最下面输入我们刚刚的CSS<br><img src=\"/images%5C1%5C4.png\"></p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote danger\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M19.76 5.23C15.84 5.23 12 2 12 2C12 2 8.15996 5.23 4.23996 5.23C4.23996 5.23 1.86996 16.99 12 22C22.13 16.99 19.76 5.23 19.76 5.23Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 16H12\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">特别注意</p>\n<p>不要破坏css原文件，请备好文件</p>\n</div>\n<p>这样我们CSS就部署完成了</p>\n<h6 id=\"废话模式\"><a href=\"#废话模式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"废话模式\"></a>废话模式</h6><p>接下来我们要在我们插件的页面中使用他<br>你不要告诉我你不会创建文档吧<br>和刚搭建hexo一样他会生成一个hexo标题文档<br>那个就是文档位置<br>我们在   <a>source</a> 文件中找到   <a>_posts</a> 文件加在这个文件里面创建随便名字的   <a>.md</a> 文件<br>然后打开这个.MD文件</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">---\ntitle: 测试 #!这是标题\ndate: 2020-08-15 18:49:36\ntags: #!这是标签\n  - 测试\ncategories: #!这是分类\n  - 动态\ncover: &#x2F;images&#x2F;shouye3342.jpg #!这是嵌入封面的设置，如果你是网页图片直接输入网页链接即可\n---<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>这就是创建文档的全部过程</p>\n<h4 id=\"嵌入视频\"><a href=\"#嵌入视频\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"嵌入视频\"></a>嵌入视频</h4><p>   <a>这里拿水水最近的视频举例</a><br>我们创建好文档之后可以用这个代码在文档下面嵌入视频</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&lt;div align&#x3D;&quot;center&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;aspect-ratio&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;iframe\n    src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;&#x2F;player.bilibili.com&#x2F;player.html?aid&#x3D;862285427&amp;bvid&#x3D;BV1kG4y11765&amp;cid&#x3D;950544529&amp;page&#x3D;1&quot;\n    scrolling&#x3D;&quot;no&quot;\n    border&#x3D;&quot;0&quot;\n    frameborder&#x3D;&quot;no&quot;\n    framespacing&#x3D;&quot;0&quot;\n    high_quality&#x3D;&quot;1&quot;\n    danmaku&#x3D;&quot;1&quot;\n    allowfullscreen&#x3D;&quot;true&quot;\n  &gt;&lt;&#x2F;iframe&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>像这样</p>\n<div align=\"center\" class=\"aspect-ratio\">\n  <iframe\n    src=\"//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=862285427&bvid=BV1kG4y11765&cid=950544529&page=1\"\n    scrolling=\"no\"\n    border=\"0\"\n    frameborder=\"no\"\n    framespacing=\"0\"\n    high_quality=\"1\"\n    danmaku=\"1\"\n    allowfullscreen=\"true\"\n  ></iframe>\n</div>\n\n<p>怎么替换视频呢？<br>打个比方，我们现在在啊B那边找一个喜欢的视频<br><img src=\"/images%5C1%5C5.png\"><br>然后我们我们鼠标移动到   <a>分享</a> 这里会出现很多中分享其中有一个嵌入的按钮<br><img src=\"/images%5C1%5C6.png\"><br>我们点击嵌入按钮，获得代码</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&lt;iframe src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;&#x2F;player.bilibili.com&#x2F;player.html?aid&#x3D;626211355&amp;bvid&#x3D;BV1St4y1979M&amp;cid&#x3D;207428566&amp;page&#x3D;1&quot; scrolling&#x3D;&quot;no&quot; border&#x3D;&quot;0&quot; frameborder&#x3D;&quot;no&quot; framespacing&#x3D;&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen&#x3D;&quot;true&quot;&gt; &lt;&#x2F;iframe&gt;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>在这个嵌入代码里面有<a>src&#x3D;”&#x2F;&#x2F;player.bilibili.com&#x2F;player.html?aid&#x3D;626211355&amp;bvid&#x3D;BV1St4y1979M&amp;cid&#x3D;207428566&amp;page&#x3D;1”</a><br>我们复制这个   <a>src&#x3D;”</a>   后面的代码<a>&#x2F;&#x2F;player.bilibili.com&#x2F;player.html?aid&#x3D;626211355&amp;bvid&#x3D;BV1St4y1979M&amp;cid&#x3D;207428566&amp;page&#x3D;1</a><br>然后导入进我们刚刚嵌入的代码里的<a>src&#x3D;”   “</a>里面即可<br>很多嵌入代码都是复制    <a>src&#x3D;</a>   后面的代码进    <a>src&#x3D;</a>   里面<br>不管什么平台都可以嵌入</p>\n<div align=\"center\" class=\"aspect-ratio\">\n  <iframe\n    src=\"//player.bilibili.com/player.html?aid=626211355&bvid=BV1St4y1979M&cid=207428566&page=1\"\n    scrolling=\"no\"\n    border=\"0\"\n    frameborder=\"no\"\n    framespacing=\"0\"\n    high_quality=\"1\"\n    danmaku=\"1\"\n    allowfullscreen=\"true\"\n  ></iframe>\n</div>\n\n<h4 id=\"修改并添加嵌入适配代码\"><a href=\"#修改并添加嵌入适配代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改并添加嵌入适配代码\"></a>修改并添加嵌入适配代码</h4><h6 id=\"修改嵌入\"><a href=\"#修改嵌入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改嵌入\"></a>修改嵌入</h6><p>网易云嵌入</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&lt;iframe frameborder&#x3D;&quot;no&quot; border&#x3D;&quot;0&quot; marginwidth&#x3D;&quot;0&quot; marginheight&#x3D;&quot;0&quot; width&#x3D;330 height&#x3D;86 src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;&#x2F;music.163.com&#x2F;outchain&#x2F;player?type&#x3D;2&amp;id&#x3D;29004400&amp;auto&#x3D;1&amp;height&#x3D;66&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;iframe&gt;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=330 height=86 src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=29004400&auto=1&height=66\"></iframe>\n用哔哩哔哩视频设备代码嵌入的话是这样的\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&lt;div align&#x3D;&quot;center&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;aspect-ratio&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;iframe\n    src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;&#x2F;music.163.com&#x2F;outchain&#x2F;player?type&#x3D;2&amp;id&#x3D;29004400&amp;auto&#x3D;1&amp;height&#x3D;66&quot;\n    scrolling&#x3D;&quot;no&quot;\n    border&#x3D;&quot;0&quot;\n    frameborder&#x3D;&quot;no&quot;\n    framespacing&#x3D;&quot;0&quot;\n    high_quality&#x3D;&quot;1&quot;\n    danmaku&#x3D;&quot;1&quot;\n    allowfullscreen&#x3D;&quot;true&quot;\n  &gt;&lt;&#x2F;iframe&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<div align=\"center\" class=\"aspect-ratio\">\n  <iframe\n    src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=29004400&auto=1&height=66\"\n    scrolling=\"no\"\n    border=\"0\"\n    frameborder=\"no\"\n    framespacing=\"0\"\n    high_quality=\"1\"\n    danmaku=\"1\"\n    allowfullscreen=\"true\"\n  ></iframe>\n</div>\n\n<p>所以这段CSS这是用于视频嵌入</p>\n<h6 id=\"添加嵌入适配代码\"><a href=\"#添加嵌入适配代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"添加嵌入适配代码\"></a>添加嵌入适配代码</h6><p>当然我们可以在刚才css代码文件添加一条</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\"> &#x2F;*100百分比展示*&#x2F;\n.aspect2-ratio &#123;\n   position: relative;\n   width: 100%;\n   height: auto;\n   padding-bottom: 100%;\n   margin: 3% auto;\n   text-align: center;\n &#125;\n .aspect2-ratio iframe &#123;\n   position: absolute;\n   width: 100%;\n   height: 100%;\n   left: 0;\n   top: 0;\n &#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>像这样<br><img src=\"/images%5C1%5C7.png\"><br>然后呢我们就可以在文档输入这条嵌入代码</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&lt;div align2&#x3D;&quot;center&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;aspect2-ratio&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;iframe\n    src&#x3D;&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;music.163.com&#x2F;playlist?id&#x3D;8003035101&amp;userid&#x3D;1411135638&quot;\n    scrolling&#x3D;&quot;no&quot;\n    border&#x3D;&quot;0&quot;\n    frameborder&#x3D;&quot;no&quot;\n    framespacing&#x3D;&quot;0&quot;\n    high_quality&#x3D;&quot;1&quot;\n    danmaku&#x3D;&quot;1&quot;\n    allowfullscreen&#x3D;&quot;true&quot;\n  &gt;&lt;&#x2F;iframe&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div align2=\"center\" class=\"aspect2-ratio\">\n  <iframe\n    src=\"https://music.163.com/playlist?id=8003035101&userid=1411135638\"\n    scrolling=\"no\"\n    border=\"0\"\n    frameborder=\"no\"\n    framespacing=\"0\"\n    high_quality=\"1\"\n    danmaku=\"1\"\n    allowfullscreen=\"true\"\n  ></iframe>\n</div>\n\n<p>或者这样的</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&lt;div align2&#x3D;&quot;center&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;aspect2-ratio&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;iframe\n    src&#x3D;&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.bilibili.com&quot;\n    scrolling&#x3D;&quot;1&quot;\n    border&#x3D;&quot;0&quot;\n    frameborder&#x3D;&quot;1&quot;\n    framespacing&#x3D;&quot;0&quot;\n    high_quality&#x3D;&quot;1&quot;\n    danmaku&#x3D;&quot;1&quot;\n    allowfullscreen&#x3D;&quot;true&quot;\n  &gt;&lt;&#x2F;iframe&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div align2=\"center\" class=\"aspect2-ratio\">\n  <iframe\n    src=\"https://www.bilibili.com\"\n    scrolling=\"1\"\n    border=\"0\"\n    frameborder=\"1\"\n    framespacing=\"0\"\n    high_quality=\"1\"\n    danmaku=\"1\"\n    allowfullscreen=\"true\"\n  ></iframe>\n</div>\n\n<h6 id=\"以此类推我们在添加几条条css\"><a href=\"#以此类推我们在添加几条条css\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"以此类推我们在添加几条条css\"></a>以此类推我们在添加几条条css</h6><pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\"> &#x2F;*小窗*&#x2F;\n.aspect3-ratio &#123;\n   position: relative;\n   width: 70%;\n   height: auto;\n   padding-bottom: 90%;\n   margin: 0% auto;\n   text-align: center;\n &#125;\n .aspect3-ratio iframe &#123;\n   position: absolut